1. Initialize empty map {}
2. Process 'a': map{'a':1}
3. Process 'a': map{'a':2}
4. Process 'b': map{'a':2,'b':1}
5. Process 'b': map{'a':2,'b':2}
6. Process 'b': map{'a':2,'b':3}
7. Process 'c': map{'a':2,'b':3,'c':1}
Result: character 'a' appears 2 times, 'b' 3 times, 'c' 1 time

1. Start: {}
2. Add 'x': {'x':1}
3. Add 'y': {'x':1,'y':1}
4. Add 'x': {'x':2,'y':1}
To remove 'x': decrement count to {'x':1,'y':1}
To remove 'y': decrement count to {'x':1,'y':0}

1. Start: freq={}
2. char='a': freq.get('a',0)=0 → freq={'a':1}
3. char='a': freq.get('a',0)=1 → freq={'a':2}
4. char='b': freq.get('b',0)=0 → freq={'a':2,'b':1}
5. char='b': freq.get('b',0)=1 → freq={'a':2,'b':2}
6. char='c': freq.get('c',0)=0 → freq={'a':2,'b':2,'c':1}
